{"text":"Shipped the `ProductDrawer` slide-over at `src/app/components/admin/ProductDrawer.tsx` and wired the "Add New Product" button to open it. The drawer mounts via a fixed overlay (so background layout never shifts), animates with the exact 250ms `cubic-bezier(0.32, 0.72, 0, 1)` choreography on both transform and opacity, and ships with a drag-and-drop media zone, an English/Bangla name pair, an inline category dropdown, tabular-num price/stock fields with the 2px `accent/blue` focus ring, and a sticky gold/ghost action footer. Escape-to-close and click-outside-to-dismiss are wired up.

- Next: hook the row Edit icon to open the drawer in edit mode with prefilled state.
- Next: add field validation + a toast confirmation on Save Product.","textMode":"visible_message"}

{"text":"Wired everything: the row Edit icon now opens the drawer prefilled with that product's data and swaps the title to `Edit [Product Name]` (with Bangla font detection for the title), the Save button blocks submission when Product Name or Base Price are empty/invalid — rendering a 1px `accent-rose` border plus a micro-caps error caption beneath the field — and on a valid save the drawer slides out while the bottom-right `SuccessToast` molecule fires ~180ms later, rising 20px with a 300ms `cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)` curve, surface-elevated background, `border-white/10`, an Emerald check with a pulsing ring, and auto-dismissing after 3s.

- Next: persist edits back to the products list (currently stateless mock).
- Next: add a destructive confirm dialog wired to the row Trash button using the same toast pattern.","textMode":"visible_message"}

{"text":"Full CRUD lifecycle is locked in. `products` is now React state — drawer Saves upsert into the array (edits patch in place, creates prepend with a generated ID, auto-derived initials, palette color, and Bangla-font auto-detection), and the grid re-renders instantly. The Trash button opens `ConfirmDeleteModal` (centered, 400px max, `bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm` overlay, 200ms ease-out scale 0.96→1, dynamic `Delete [Product Name]?` title with Bangla font support, and a Rose-accented Delete action). On confirm the row drops from state and the toast fires ~180ms later in destructive variant: Rose icon ring, Rose-tinted border, "Deleted" eyebrow, and the "[Product Name] deleted" message.

- Next: persist `products` to `localStorage` so refreshes survive.
- Next: add a bulk-select column with multi-delete that aggregates into one toast.","textMode":"visible_message"}

